metadata.name: Genesis Trip NFT Ticket: Peru 2022 #1/10
metadata.description: The official NFT ticket for Destination Dao's genesis trip to Peru May 2-7 2022. If Rainbow Mountain and Machu Picchu in Peru aren't at the top of your Bucket List, they definitely should be! Join Destination's founders Elliott and Jonny and other like-minded travellers on an epic six-day adventure in Peru. For more information regarding the trip please visit www.destinationdao.xyz/peru.
